    <body>
      <section eId="sec_160_GGG">
        <num>160-GGG</num>
        <heading>Plan of operation</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GGG__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish procedures for collecting and managing the assets of the\nfund;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GGG__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish regular places and times for meetings of the fund's\nboard of directors;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GGG__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish accounting and record-keeping procedures for all\nfinancial transactions of the fund, its agents and the board of\ndirectors;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GGG__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establish a procedure for determining and collecting the\nappropriate amount of assessments under this article; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_160_GGG__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>contain such additional provisions as the board of directors of\nthe fund may deem necessary or proper for the execution of the powers\nand duties of the fund.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
